Status Text
Time Sequences
Next timer ring probability
Different types of repeat probabilities (binomial dist, etc)
different sound env variables
    $PyTimerAlarm[var] is the environment variable for the sound file to be played
     where var is given to the -sound arg
     E.g. timer 5 -sound 1 ---> timer of 5 minutes playing sound at file $PyTimerAlarm1
          timer 7 -s -sound Short ---> timer of 7 seconds playing sound at file $PyTimerAlarmShort


Verbose Levels
    0-none
    1-Just time
    2-Full Status

